		<td width="100%" class="newssubject" colspan=2><a name="news_6984"></a>Upcoming Downtime Specifics<br>
			<font class="smallcomments">[ <a href="/forums/showthread.php?threadid=6984" class="smallcommentshi">add comment</a> ] submitted by: Kaladdar</font><br>
		</td>
