		<td width="100%" class="newssubject" colspan=2><a name="news_6917"></a>09/27/02 Patch Message<br>
			<font class="smallcomments">[ <a href="/forums/showthread.php?threadid=6917" class="smallcommentshi">2 comments</a> ] submitted by: Marcin</font><br>
		</td>
