	<tr>
		<td width="15">&nbsp;</td>
		<td>
<br>
September 27, 2002  1:00 am<br />
------------------------------<br />
<br />
This patch fixes a number of issues that first arose in yesterday's patch.  We apologise for the additional downtime.  <br />
<br />
- Zones should be considerably more stable.<br />
<br />
- Item links no longer cause display lockups.<br />
<br />
- NPCs once again choose their targets properly.<br />
<br />
- Gravity Flux-type spells again function properly.<br />
<br />
- The Guildmasters of Sanctus Seru are no longer quite as mean as they were previously.<br />
<br />
- Ring of Flamewarding is again wearable by Wizards.  <br />
<br />
<br />
Thank you for your patience, and have a good weekend!<br />
<br />
- The EverQuest Team</td>
